# Commit Message Template for Wix Studio Azure Platform
#
# Please follow the conventional commit format:
# <type>[optional scope]: <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore, revert
# 
# Examples:
# feat(auth): add OIDC authentication for Azure
# fix(docker): resolve npm ci issue in api-services build
# docs: update deployment guide with OIDC setup
# ci: add environment-specific deployment workflows
#
# Use commit flags for deployment:
# [dev] - triggers development deployment
# [staging] - triggers staging deployment  
# [prod] - triggers production deployment
#
# This commit will be GPG signed automatically.
